reviewText:
Complete overuse of different camera angles for no other reason than to display rich peoples' houses. The actors are a bunch of one-dimensional "fresas". The movie seems to only want to portray the ridiculous lives of excess that the rich experience in Mexico.
I was sick and tired of hearing the  "fresa" /condescending accent of the main characters that I had to stop mid way through the film.
I liked the movie. Story is entertaining, but the script/story is not an award winning product. Good for entertainment purposes only.
